text: A nice pub with a Good sound system! Staff r attentive and friendly. Def a place with the nice crowd who love to sing too! Will def go again!

This lounge has the best karaoke system and service. I've been here a few times, thanks to a friend who invited me, and it's always a blast! The people are warm and welcoming, the environment is clean, and everyone is just here to have a good time. The pub really attracts the right crowd, which makes the experience even better. Highly recommend!
